---
/**
 * /gift-cards — gift card info page.
 *
 * Live twistedpin.com/gift-cards/ returns 404 — the page DOESN'T
 * exist on the current site. But the live FAQ confirms gift cards
 * ARE sold:
 *   - "available to purchase in-store at the front desk"
 *   - "valid on bowling and arcade related purchases in our facility"
 *   - (no online purchase option)
 *
 * So this page exists to surface that fact for users who land on
 * /gift-cards/ via search or the MORE/drawer. It explains the
 * in-store-only flow and points users to visit.
 *
 * Voice rule check: "cheap/discount/value/deals/budget-friendly"
 * hard-banned per CLAUDE.md Working Preferences. Gift cards aren't
 * discount language — they're a purchase product. Frame as "give
 * the night, not a coupon" — premium-positioning angle.
 *
 * TODOs (non-blocking):
 *   - Confirm with ops: are there standard denominations? Custom
 *     amounts? Both? Currently hand-waved to "any amount" pending
 *     verification.
 *   - "valid on bowling and arcade related purchases" — does NOT
 *     include food/drinks per the live FAQ. Surfaced clearly so
 *     gift recipients aren't surprised.
 *   - Future: online purchase via a gift card platform (Toast,
 *     Square, etc.) — would graduate this page from info-only to
 *     a transactional page.
 */
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
import SnapFooter from "../components/snap/SnapFooter.astro";
---
<Base
  title="Gift Cards — Twisted Pin Plainfield IL"
  description="Twisted Pin gift cards — available in-store at the front desk. Valid for bowling and arcade. Plainfield, IL."
>

  <section class="t2-hero" data-hero aria-labelledby="giftcards-h1">
    <div class="t2-hero-copy">
      <p class="t-eyebrow hero-fade" data-delay-ms="0">Gift Cards</p>
      <h1 class="t-display t2-hero-headline hero-fade" id="giftcards-h1" data-delay-ms="120">
        Give the night.
      </h1>
      <p class="t2-hero-sub hero-fade" data-delay-ms="320">
        Twisted Pin gift cards — available at the front desk. Good
        for bowling and arcade.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="t2-section" aria-labelledby="giftcards-h2">
    <div class="t2-section-inner">
      <h2 class="t-eyebrow" id="giftcards-h2" style="font-size:11px;">How It Works</h2>
      <p class="t2-section-body">
        Stop by the front desk during open hours and pick up a gift
        card in any amount. We don't sell them online (yet) — it's
        an in-person stop.
      </p>

      <p class="t2-section-body">
        <strong>What gift cards cover:</strong> bowling and arcade
        purchases at Twisted Pin. They don't cover food or bar tabs —
        those are settled the regular way at checkout.
      </p>

      <p class="t2-section-body">
        We're at <a href="#find-us">15610 S Joliet Rd, Plainfield, IL</a>.
        Footer shows current hours.
      </p>

      <p class="t2-section-body">
        Looking for a group experience instead of a card?
        <a href="https://twistedevents.zite.so/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Plan an event →</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <SnapFooter />
</Base>
